      "content": "but the juice made me feel even worse and now i feel like i might pass out. i'm scared if i just keep eating sugar my levels will spike way too high and that's also dangerous right? wouldn't it be safer and more effective to just do a tiny corrective dose of insulin now to keep things level while i wait for the sugar to kick in? i just want to stabilize.",
